### Hadith 4:340

*Narrated Abu Burda:*

'Aisha brought out to us a patched wool Len garment, and she said, "(It
chanced that) the soul of Allah's Apostle was taken away while he was
wearing this." Abu-Burda added, "Aisha brought out to us a thick waist
sheet like the ones made by the Yemenites, and also a garment of the
type called Al-Mulabbada."

